misc.label: Capabilities
description:
The read-only set of capabilities available for the current UI session.
Capabilities are simple key-value pairs of (string, boolean), where the string denotes the capability ID,
and the boolean is a flag indicating if the capability is enabled or disabled.
signature: { [key: string]: Record<string, boolean | Record<string, boolean>>; navLinks: Record<string, boolean>; management: { [sectionId: string]: Record<string, boolean>; }; catalogue: Record<string, boolean>; } & { discover?: {} | undefined; dashboard?: {} | undefined; maps?: {} | undefined; visualize?: {} | undefined; }
